'''2001年英國大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2001 British Grand Prix}}），是[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]在2001年7月15日舉辦的賽事。比賽總計60圈，將在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[白金漢郡|白金漢郡]]與[[北安普敦郡|北安普敦郡]][[銀石|銀石]]的[[銀石賽道|銀石賽道]]舉行。這是[[2001年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2001年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]的第11場分站賽事，同時也是第56屆[[英國大獎賽|英國大獎賽]]。最終由[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫車隊]]的[[米卡·海基寧|米卡·海基寧]]獲得冠軍。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport/hi/english/static/motorsport/formula_one/results_and_fixtures.stm#British%20Grand%20Prix |title=Formula One results and fixtures |work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |publisher=[[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation]] |accessdate=2009-06-25 |date=2000-07-03 |archive-date=2001-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010611131729/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport/hi/english/static/motorsport/formula_one/results_and_fixtures.stm#British%20Grand%20Prix |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[法拉利車隊|法拉利車隊]]的[[麥可·舒馬克|麥可·舒馬克]]獲得亞軍，而其隊友[[魯本斯·巴里切羅|魯本斯·巴里切羅]]取得第三名。<ref name = "BBC race">{{cite news |first=Andrew |last=Benson |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/1440098.stm |title=Hakkinen halts Schumacher charge |work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |publisher=[[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation]] |date=2001-07-15 |accessdate=2009-06-23 |archive-date=2004-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040510194750/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/1440098.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>這是海基寧本季的首場分站冠軍。

這場比賽共有5位車手退賽，首圈[[喬丹車隊|喬丹]]的[[亞諾·楚理|亞諾·楚理]]與[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫]]的[[大衛·庫塔_(賽車手)|大衛·庫塔]]在1號彎發生碰撞；[[英美車隊|英美車隊]]的[[傑克·維倫紐夫|傑克·維倫紐夫]]在起跑時把隊友[[奧利維耶·潘尼斯|奧利維耶·潘尼斯]]逼出賽道，迫使潘尼斯退賽；[[拉夫·舒馬克|拉夫·舒馬克]]和[[盧恰諾·布爾蒂|盧恰諾·布爾蒂]]同樣未能完賽。[[塔爾索·馬克斯|塔爾索·馬克斯]]本賽首次未獲參賽資格，因為他未符合[[107%規則|107%規則]]。<ref name = "BBC qualifying">{{cite news |first=Andrew |last=Benson |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/1438792.stm |title=Schumacher grabs pole |work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |publisher=[[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation]] |date=2001-07-14 |accessdate=2009-06-23 |archive-date=2004-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040731055953/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/1438792.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>這是[[海因茨-哈拉爾德·弗倫岑|海因茨-哈拉爾德·弗倫岑]]最後一次為[[喬丹車隊|喬丹車隊]]出賽，他在本季的表現令人失望，於賽後被車隊解雇，且在下一場比賽[[2001年德國大獎賽|2001年德國大獎賽]]坐冷板凳。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/3009551/Frentzen-sacked-by-Jordan.html |title=Frentzen sacked by Jordan |work=Telegraph Online |publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|Telegraph Publishing Group]] |date=2001-07-25 |accessdate=2009-06-23 |archive-date=2011-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110116063943/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/3009551/Frentzen-sacked-by-Jordan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/1457107.stm |title=Frentzen: The man behind the wheel |work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |publisher=[[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation]] |date=2001-07-25 |accessdate=2009-06-23 |archive-date=2002-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021203100829/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/1457107.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

